'''豌豆蛋白'''是一種從豌豆分離出的蛋白質原料，主要用來製作奶類替代食品，例如非奶製純素[[起司|起司]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.daiyafoods.com/our-products/cheddar-wedge|title=CHEDDAR STYLE WEDGE|accessdate=14 July 2013|work=daiyafoods.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728224136/http://www.daiyafoods.com/our-products/cheddar-wedge|archivedate=2013年7月28日}}</ref> 和[[優格|優格]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323820304578410540563066644.html?mod=dist_smartbrief|title=Label Decoder {{!}} Protein Additives|accessdate=14 July 2013|work=Wall Street Journal|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004232705/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323820304578410540563066644.html?mod=dist_smartbrief|dead-url=no}}</ref> 它主要是從黃色[[豌豆|豌豆]](學名''[[豌豆|Pisum sativum]])'' 所萃取，並含有典型的豆類[[胺基酸|胺基酸]]。

不同種的豌豆株的會影響蛋白質的特性。<ref name="BaracCabrilo2010">{{Cite journal|title=Profile and Functional Properties of Seed Proteins from Six Pea (Pisum sativum) Genotypes|last=Barac|first=Miroljub|last2=Cabrilo|first2=Slavica|journal=International Journal of Molecular Sciences|issue=12|doi=10.3390/ijms11124973|year=2010|volume=11|pages=4973–4990|issn=1422-0067|last3=Pesic|first3=Mirjana|last4=Stanojevic|first4=Sladjana|last5=Zilic|first5=Sladjana|last6=Macej|first6=Ognjen|last7=Ristic|first7=Nikola}}</ref> 豌豆蛋白分離出的豆球蛋白，其特性有些類似於[[酪蛋白|酪蛋白]]，因此豌豆蛋白製品常被用來替代[[乳清蛋白|乳清蛋白]]食品。<ref name="OverduinGuérin-Deremaux2015">{{cite journal|title=NUTRALYS®pea protein: characterization ofin vitrogastric digestion andin vivogastrointestinal peptide responses relevant to satiety|last2=Guérin-Deremaux|first2=Laetitia|journal=Food & Nutrition Research|issue=0|doi=10.3402/fnr.v59.25622|year=2015|volume=59|issn=1654-661X|last3=Wils|first3=Daniel|last4=Lambers|first4=Tim T.|last1=Overduin|first1=Joost}}</ref><ref name="BabaultPaïzis2015">{{cite journal|title=Pea proteins oral supplementation promotes muscle thickness gains during resistance training: a double-blind, randomized, Placebo-controlled clinical trial vs. Whey protein|last2=Païzis|first2=Christos|journal=Journal of the International Society of Sports Nutrition|issue=1|doi=10.1186/s12970-014-0064-5|year=2015|volume=12|pages=3|issn=1550-2783|last3=Deley|first3=Gaëlle|last4=Guérin-Deremaux|first4=Laetitia|last5=Saniez|first5=Marie-Hélène|last6=Lefranc-Millot|first6=Catherine|last7=Allaert|first7=François A|last1=Babault|first1=Nicolas}}</ref> 由於消費者對大豆製品可能為[[基因改造|基因改造]]而有所顧慮，豌豆蛋白食品的有些行銷訴求就是用來取代大豆製品。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2014/feb/14/silicon-valley-hack-food-industry|title=Why Silicon Valley wants to hack the food industry|author=Sydney Brownstone|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2017-03-14|archive-date=2017-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213083038/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2014/feb/14/silicon-valley-hack-food-industry|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theepochtimes.com/n3/1949098-how-pea-protein-became-a-star-ingredient/|title=Mushy Peas? Not Anymore. Peas Are a Superfood!|date=27 January 2016|work=The Epoch Times|accessdate=2017-03-14|archive-date=2017-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610172221/http://www.theepochtimes.com/n3/1949098-how-pea-protein-became-a-star-ingredient/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

